# shadcn-form-agent conventions

- Use picocolors for terminal output — NOT winston or other logging libraries.
- Screenshots: save to ./screenshots/ (gitignored) AND return base64 in tool responses.
- Browser default: HEADED mode (headless: false).
- No form submission logic — coordinate and observe only.
- Use Playwright direct Node.js API — NOT MCP browser tools.
- Coordinate-driven workflow: agent navigates by x/y coordinates, not DOM selectors.
- Pin @openai/agents to 0.0.x — do not upgrade to 0.1+ without explicit approval.
